{"tid":1815081,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】有個黐線佬派福袋呀 !","createTime":"2020-01-07T09:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T03:23:10.000Z","uid":121029,"like":125,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"c55053f2561ac9957f4cf14733b17532b4a59fe3","tid":1815081,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的，之前一直收到好多好心嘅商戶捐左好多衫出嚟。而各位手足發夢時都做足準備，所以D衫就積存咗喺到。衫大多數係全新，有T-SHIRT , 風褸 ,運動褲同全新SPORTS BRA。款式都係大眾款式為主，顏色有雜色和黑色都有。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新年就到，我想各位仔仔女女都有新衫過年，所以決定將衣物製成福袋送比有需要嘅仔女。詳情如下：<br />\n&mdash;📌仔女請填妥GOOGLE表格報尺寸<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;📍領取方法於表格內三個活動時間交收<br />\n（理大廚房佬大食會day1 &amp;DAY2 ） <br />\n (年三十於旺角舉辦的-離地年宵- )<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;📌福袋有咩架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男女裝福袋各有6個衣物ITEMS，女裝於表格內可選裙子。<br />\n想取意頭大富大貴，所以儘量包含運動褲一條。<br />\n<br />\n－📌D衫發夢合唔合用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n福袋內衣物以運動類型為主，6個ITEM內包一件黑色上衣<br />\n<br />\nPS :‼️嚟緊我地嘅街站唔會拎衣物出去派，因為濟銷之餘，寧願派其他更合用嘅嘢物資<br />\n<br />\nPS2: ‼️女裝會由女手足處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS3:‼️好重要! 好重要! 好重要 ! 希望大家收到D衫唔好嘘，唔好嫌棄。呢D衣物本來係方便你地替換，我地經歷左水炮車D水洗唔甩之餘，仲好乸皮膚。請大家好好使用D衣物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS4:‼️黐線佬唔好問有冇SPORTS BRA 拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs5:‼️暫時得三個活動有義工幫手派福袋，所以日子只有呢三日揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n表格: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/ks9ijbXLaxb1TgAh6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fks9ijbXLaxb1TgAh6&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=2d3e9032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/ks9ijbXLaxb1TgAh6</a><br />\n活動: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100752791448638/posts/109505910573326/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100752791448638%2Fposts%2F109505910573326%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=771988f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100752791448638/posts/109505910573326/?d=n</a><br />\n活動: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/feverfes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffeverfes%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=f7324b0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/feverfes/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9004eee933d92a4dc18539cabcae58e56f4edc0f","tid":1815081,"uid":314399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6a848a337aa10a42566e22c54081e0c697a16e8","tid":1815081,"uid":59908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e1730698915768620727b64c73839839f4f71221","tid":1815081,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推"},{"pid":"01f661d207b4c3f354b39c82fb3058f10c53e63c","tid":1815081,"uid":275162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:28:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"661c804ad6be456950b04696077ed661baa8d41f","tid":1815081,"uid":138594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac2ada51dfaefb75291a06aafcbc0446f5920ae8","tid":1815081,"uid":281704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0